data.title: Office of the Dean of the Faculty
data.meta_description: Experience Princeton’s history of scholarly innovation through our collection of emeriti bios.
data.meta_site_name: Office of the Dean of the Faculty
data.text: Princeton University takes great pride in our esteemed faculty emeriti, each of whom has made their mark both on the University and in their fields. Across notable scholarly careers pursued with intellectual curiosity, distinguished heights of research and teaching, and a track record of groundbreaking accomplishments, their achievements are many — and their contributions often extend well beyond their years of active service. Here, we invite you to learn more about their work.
